{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"🖱️ 侧边Dock\n      左侧或底部悬浮图标式导航，像macOS Dock。极简、不占空间、有格调。","choice":"nav-side-dock","id":null,"timestamp":1782214187348}
{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"Latte\n        \n          首页\n          博客\n        \n      \n    \n    \n      🫧 悬浮毛玻璃\n      导航栏独立悬浮，与内容区域分离，圆角毛玻璃卡片式。留出呼吸感。","choice":"nav-floating-glass","id":null,"timestamp":1782214199126}
